<p>'The hat. So Californian! Love this whole look really,' enthused one, while a second agreed: 'Oh I just love this look on her! So effortlessly glamorous.'</p>

<p>A third added: 'Killing this look. Love it!' while a further commented: 'Love love love this look.'</p>

